Detailed Description

cvmx_lmc::_dimm_ctl

Note that this CSR is only used when LMC()_CONTROL[RDIMM_ENA] = 1. During a power-up/init sequence, this CSR controls LMC's write operations to the control words in the JEDEC standard DDR3 SSTE32882 registering clock driver or DDR4 Register DDR4RCD01 on an RDIMM.
